<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得像這樣子，
有人來自己家裡玩，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很開心呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">偶爾像這樣子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />悠閒地待在房間裡<delay8 />
也不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挑選家具時，品味可是很重要的喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛開始一個人住的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也常常選錯家具呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />布置房間的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的果然還是壁紙吧！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得<delay8 />從壁紙就能看出屋主的品味呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是能生活在
自己喜愛的家具的懷抱中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就很讓人心情雀躍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你們居然會在同一個時間來我家玩，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太巧了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請放輕鬆，把這裡當成自己家吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟多一點客人才熱鬧，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也很開心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然會在同一個時間來我家玩……<delay20 />
你和<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還真是有默契呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天大家要一起玩得高興點唷！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得這樣好像在開家庭派對一樣，<delay8 />
很讓人興奮呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和朋友在一起真的好開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />常常不小心就玩到忘了時間呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是家裡一直都像今天一樣熱鬧，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該是多快樂的事呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然打掃起來應該會很辛苦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>